Problem 3 - Caesar Cipher
by Lars Gröber, Robert Söder, Hendrik Edelmann

Directory structure:

    |--src
    |  |--main.cpp      # main source file
    |  |--Cipher.cpp    # implementation of class Cipher
    |--inc
       |--Cipher.h      # header file for class Cipher


How to run:

cd build
cmake .. && make && ./caesar_cipher     # cmake 3.5 or up required

or

g++ -o caesar_cipher inc/*.h src/*.cpp && ./caesar_cipher
